
# 30 Swift Projects â€“ Inspired by 100 Days of Swift (UIKit)

This repository contains **30 Swift projects** inspired by Paul Hudsonâ€™s [100 Days of Swift (UIKit)](https://www.hackingwithswift.com/100).  
Each project introduces new iOS development concepts, UIKit components, or Apple frameworks, helping you build a strong foundation in Swift and iOS development.

---

## ðŸš€ Projects Overview

| Day / Project | Title                  | Key Concepts & Learning Goals                                                                                                                |
| ------------- | ---------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **1**         | Storm Viewer           | FileManager, `resourcePath`, `contentsOfDirectory`, `UITableViewController`, `UITableViewCell`, `UIImageView`, view controller instantiation |
| **2**         | Guess the Flag         | Layout design, `CALayer`, `IBAction`, randomization                                                                                          |
| **3**         | Share Image App        | `UIBarButtonItem`, `UIActivityViewController`, sharing images                                                                                |
| **4**         | Web Browser            | `WKWebView`, `UIAlertController` action sheets, `UIToolbar`, `UIProgressView`                                                                |
| **5**         | Word Scramble          | Reading from disk, `UIAlertController`, `IndexPath`                                                                                          |
| **6**         | Auto Layout            | Auto Layout basics, constraints, Visual Format Language                                                                                      |
| **7**         | Whitehouse Petitions   | `UITabBarController`, JSON handling, networking, data decoding with `Codable`                                                                |
| **8**         | 7 Swifty Words         | Programmatic UI, text alignment, layout margins, custom fonts                                                                                |
| **9**         | Grand Central Dispatch | GCD, threading, `perform(_:with:afterDelay:)`                                                                                                |
| **10**        | Names to Faces         | `UICollectionView`, `UIImagePickerController`, subclassing `NSObject`                                                                        |
| **11**        | Pachinko               | `SpriteKit`, nodes, touch handling, physics bodies, `SKAction`, collisions, particle emitters                                                |
| **12**        | User Defaults          | Using `UserDefaults`, JSON serialization, `NSCoding`, `Codable`                                                                              |
| **13**        | Instafilter            | Image filtering, Core Image, applying `CIFilter` to photos                                                                                   |
| **14**        | Whack-a-Penguin        | `SpriteKit`, `SKCropNode`, `SKAction`, randomness, touch handling                                                                            |
| **15**        | Animation Playground   | UIKit animations, `CGAffineTransform`, `UIView.animate`, spring animations                                                                   |
| **16**        | Capital Cities         | `MKMapView`, `MKAnnotation`, `CLLocationCoordinate2D`, `UIAlertController`                                                                   |
| **17**        | Space Race             | `SpriteKit`, scrolling backgrounds, `SKPhysicsContactDelegate`, collision detection                                                          |
| **18**        | Debugging              | Debugging techniques, `assert()`, breakpoints, `print()`                                                                                     |
| **19**        | JavaScript Injection   | `WKWebView`, `WKUserScript`, Safari extensions, injecting JavaScript                                                                         |
| **20**        | Fireworks Night        | `CAEmitterLayer`, particle emitters, Core Animation                                                                                          |
| **21**        | Local Notifications    | `UNUserNotificationCenter`, scheduling notifications, handling actions                                                                       |
| **22**        | Detect-a-Beacon        | Core Location, `CLBeaconRegion`, Bluetooth iBeacon detection                                                                                 |
| **23**        | Swifty Ninja           | `SpriteKit`, slicing with `UIBezierPath`, particle effects, physics                                                                          |
| **24**        | Swift Strings          | Advanced `String` APIs, substrings, Unicode, performance                                                                                     |
| **25**        | Selfie Share           | Multipeer Connectivity, sending images/text between devices                                                                                  |
| **26**        | Marble Maze            | `SpriteKit`, `CMMotionManager`, accelerometer, physics-based gameplay                                                                        |
| **27**        | Core Graphics          | Drawing with Core Graphics, `UIGraphicsImageRenderer`, blend modes, text drawing                                                             |
| **28**        | Secret Swift           | Keychain, biometric authentication (`Touch ID` / `Face ID`), secure storage                                                                  |
| **29**        | Exploding Monkeys      | `SpriteKit`, projectiles, destructible terrain, `SKTexture`                                                                                  |
| **30**        | Instruments            | Performance tuning with Instruments, memory leaks, Time Profiler                                                                             |
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

